er.avif?t=1730351683\" width=406 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/afd0fea6240e3bba0ced5488683a65de.webm?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/afd0fea6240e3bba0ced5488683a65de.mp4?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually open new locations, upgrade your equipment, and offer additional services. Grow your laundromat business step by step, adapting to customer needs along the way and improve your store’s rating.</p>",
